[[File:Moriya Family Tree - 守矢氏系図.png|thumb|center|170px|Genealogy of the first five generations of the {{ill|Moriya clan|ja|守矢氏|1=Moriya clan|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Moriya clan|13=User:Immanuelle/Moriya clan|qq=}}]]

Katakurabe no Mikoto is the child of {{ill|Takeminakata|lt=Takeminakata|lt=Takeminakata no Kami|ja|建御名方神|1=Takeminakata|2=ja|3=タケミナカタ|lt=Takeminakata|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeminakata no Kami|qq=}} and {{ill|Yasakatome|lt=Yasakatome|lt=Yasakatome no Kami|ja|八坂刀売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yasakatome no Kami|qq=}}. While the consort is unknown, Katakurabe no Mikoto is said to have three children: {{ill|Kodamahiko-no-Mikoto|ja|児玉彦命|1=Kodamahiko-no-Mikoto|2=ja|3=児玉彦命|lt=Kodamahiko-no-Mikoto|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kodamahiko no Mikoto|qq=}}, {{ill|Kamitsumitama no Kami|ja|上津御玉神|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kamitsumitama no Kami|qq=}}, and {{ill|Shimotsumitama no Kami|ja|下津御玉神|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shimotsumitama no Kami|qq=}}.{{Sfn|Nobukazu|1921|pp=17–18}}

Among them, Kodamahiko no Mikoto succeeded {{ill|Chikatsugami|ja|千鹿頭神|1=Chikatō-no-Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Chikatsugami|13=User:Immanuelle/Chikatō-no-Kami|qq=}} in both religious and political roles, married {{ill|Mitsutamahime no Kami|ja|美都多麻比売神|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mitsutamahime no Kami|qq=}}, daughter of {{ill|Moritatsugami|ja|守達神|1=Moritachi no Kami|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Moritatsugami|13=User:Immanuelle/Moritachi no Kami|qq=}}, and fathered {{ill|Yakushigami|ja|八櫛神|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yakushigami|qq=}}. For this reason, Kodamahiko no Mikoto is counted as the fourth generation in the genealogical records of the {{ill|Moriya clan|ja|守矢氏|1=Moriya clan|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Moriya clan|13=User:Immanuelle/Moriya clan|qq=}}.

